  "original_title": "\u2019\u2019\u0da2\u0db1\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2\u0d9c\u0dda \u0d85\u0dc3\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dd3\u0db8\u0dda \u0dbd\u0dd2\u0db4\u0dd2\u0dba \u0dbd\u0dd0\u0db6\u0dd3 \u0db1\u0dd1: \u0db6\u0dbd\u0dcf\u0db4\u0ddc\u0dbb\u0ddc\u0dad\u0dca\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u0dc0\u0dcf\u2019\u2019",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "\"President's resignation letter not received: Waiting\"",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Speaker Mr. Mahindayapa Ebvardhana said that he has not yet received the letter of resignation of the President.",
        "Sources also state that this letter will be handed over to the Speaker this afternoon.",
        "President Gotabaya Rajapaksa recently informed the speaker that he will resign today."
      ],
